<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-dark-bg text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">About</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Built from <span class="font-medium">running it ourselves</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We're a lean team based in Macau, serving businesses across APAC. Before we sold AI Employees 
          to anyone else, we built them for ourselves — every role, every workflow, every integration.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our stack runs on Hermes Agent, an open-source AI agent framework. Each AI Employee is a 
          configured agent with a specific role, personality, tools, and schedule — deployed on its own 
          secure VPS, isolated from every other client.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We don't resell chatbots or ship generic automation. We build dedicated employees that 
          become part of your team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Macau</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/50">Based in Macau, serving APAC</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">24+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/50">AI Employee roles available</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Hermes</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/50">Built on open-source Hermes Agent</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Flat Fee</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/50">No per-task charges, no contracts</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
